_sText:
Remember the good old days...... This is a remake of the Nintendo 64 Classic Goldeneye map Complex for Counter-Strike Source! Special Thanks to Syco* for the radar overview background music testing.and publishing on this map it has been a good collabrative effort to get this polished off. This is a must for any server, there are 40 spawns, 4 hostages and 1 reccue point. works really well and adds a new dimension to an all time classic! there is also a FY version of this map available too, for deathmatch / gungame or simply a fy go here for the alternative version
fy_complex enjoy the nostalgia! Live and let live
